msgctxt "72_Tanimura"
msgid "(This is taking way too long. I need to get there, now!)"
msgstr "(He perdido demasiado tiempo. ¡Tengo que darme prisa!)"

msgctxt "144_Ueno Seiwa Clan Member"
msgid "Ngh... Argh..."
msgstr "Ngh... Argh..."

msgctxt "156_Tanimura"
msgid "Sorry, but you'll have to try harder than that."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero tendrás que echarle más ganas."

msgctxt "168_Ueno Seiwa Clan Member"
msgid "Too many... goddamn... tackles... Think I busted a rib!"
msgstr "Esto... no... ha terminado..."

msgctxt "192_Ueno Seiwa Clan Member"
msgid "Heheh... Going somewhere?"
msgstr "Je, je... ¿Adónde crees que vas?"

msgctxt "216_Tanimura"
msgid "You people really don't give up, do you? Fine... If it's a fight you want, you got it!"
msgstr "De verdad que no se dan por vencidos, ¿eh? Está bien... Si quieren pelea, ¡la tendrán!"

